    public interface ContactResult
    A ContactResult represents a set of basic contact fields returned from an external Contact Management System or Address Book. A ContactResult has methods to get all the basic fields it needs to display in the UI, as well as a few utility methods to assist in converting the result into a real Contact in BillingCenter.
